The hololive OFFICIAL CARD GAME is a trading card game with the concept of &ldquo;competition,&rdquo; in which we build and compete in this game with our fans.

Players, as fans of the talent, will produce the most impressive stage with their chosen &ldquo;Oshi holomem&rdquo; and other &ldquo;holomems&rdquo;. Players send &ldquo;cheers&rdquo; to the holomems to reach the peak of the &ldquo;hololive Exstreamer Cup.&rdquo;

Make new friends and make the most of your hololive &lsquo;Oshi&rsquo; life (or, in short, hololife&rdquo;) with the trading card game!

     &ldquo;holomems&rdquo; is the abbreviation for &ldquo;the members of hololive.&rdquo;

Don&rsquo;t rubber ducks belong in the bathtub? These rebellious rubber ducks disagree! They are completely bored of baths and would like to float, splash and dive somewhere else for once. Together, they squeakily waddle over to&hellip; the water park! Fill the various pools of the water park with rubber ducks. The more, the merrier, but full means full! After all, one duck too many, and you might find yourself in troubled waters&hellip;

Duck & Dive is a card game for 2 to 6 players, where players try to earn point by placing duck cards in pools. They do so by excavating cards from a deck hoping with every extra card it doesn't overgrow the pool. One card to many, can cause your turn to end but an perfectly full pool will earn you points. The game is about high risk/high rewards and hand management.

&mdash;description from the designer

Shinobi is the sequel to Tiago Junges' Ronin RPG, and this time you'll be in the shoes of a ninja. Through a series of missions given to you by your lord, you'll defeat your clan's enemies and learn the secret arts of the Shinobi. Your destiny will be shaped by the endless war between clans, the machinations of villains, and the hidden purpose of your ultimate enemy&hellip;

Shinobi is a solo RPG that uses the same system as Ronin. Each mission you receive is structured in a series of steps, in which conflicts and combats are resolved by dice rolls.

&mdash;description from the publisher (translated)

Shinobi es la continuaci&oacute;n del juego de rol Ronin, obra de Tiago Junges, y en esta ocasi&oacute;n te pondr&aacute;s en la piel de un ninja. A trav&eacute;s de una serie de misiones que te ser&aacute;n encargadas por tu se&ntilde;or, ir&aacute;s derrotando a los enemigos de tu clan y aprendiendo las artes secretas de los Shinobi. Tu destino quedar&aacute; marcado por la interminable guerra entre los clanes, las maquinaciones de los villanos y el prop&oacute;sito oculto de tu enemigo final&hellip;

Shinobi es un juego de rol en solitario que utiliza el mismo sistema de Ronin. Cada misi&oacute;n que recibes se estructura en una serie de pasos, en los que los conflictos y combates se resuelven mediante tiradas de dados.

&mdash;description from the publisher

CASE STORY

The night of October 27, 2023 marks a tragic event in the famous "Radovan" circus &mdash; the caravan of the famous clairvoyant Morgana was mysteriously consumed by flames. As detectives, you are called to piece together the evidence and reveal the identity of the murderer. Among the main suspects are the circus performers, who are hiding secrets from the prying eyes of the public.Will you be able to obtain and connect the necessary information to shed light on this enigmatic case? Radovan Forest? All the answers are hidden behind the circus curtain, and your mission is to bring them into the spotlight. Enter the mysterious world of Radovan Circus to bring justice to Madame Morgana, whose soul is still waiting to be avenged!

?️ Investigation game in which you take on the role of a detective to solve an unsolved case;

? Analyze evidence, eliminate suspects and identify the criminal;

? Browse social networks, check suspects' alibis, decode secret messages and discover hidden details that can change the course of the investigation;

POVESTEA CAZULUI

Noaptea de 27 octombrie 2023 marchează un eveniment tragic &icirc;n cadrul faimosului circ &bdquo;Radovan" &mdash; caravana renumitei clarvăzătoare Morgana a fost mistuită de flăcări &icirc;n mod misterios. &Icirc;n calitate de detectivi, sunteți chemați să puneți cap la cap probele și să dezvăluiți identitatea criminalului. Printre suspecții principali se numără artiștii circului, care ascund secrete departe de ochii curioși ai publicului. Veți putea obține și conecta informațiile necesare pentru a face lumină &icirc;n acest caz enigmatic? Ce legături ar putea avea moartea lui Madame Morgana cu legenda urbană a fantomei miresei ce b&acirc;ntuie pădurea Radovan? Toate răspunsurile se ascund &icirc;n spatele cortinei circului, iar misiunea voastră este să le aduceți &icirc;n lumina reflectoarelor. Intrați &icirc;n lumea misterioasă a circului Radovan pentru a face dreptate lui Madame Morgana, al cărei suflet &icirc;ncă așteaptă să fie răzbunat!

CASE STORY

On the night of March 9, 1930, a tragic event took place in the premises of the famous Obregia hospice. Igor Malenovschi, a patient locked in the maximum security room, was found dead under mysterious circumstances. As detectives, you are called upon to piece together the clues and reveal the identity of the criminal. Among the prime suspects are patients admitted to the hospice's B wing, where the most aggressive of them were kept. Will you be able to gather and connect the information needed to shed light on this enigmatic case? What could Igor Malenovschi's death have to do with his dark past? All the answers are hidden in the dark corridors of the hospice, and your mission is to bring them into the light of truth. Enter the scary world of the Obregia hospice to bring justice to Igor Malenovschi, whose secrets are still waiting to be revealed!

- Investigation game in which you take on the role of a detective to solve an unsolved case;

- Analyze evidence, eliminate suspects and identify the criminal;

- Browse social networks, check suspects' alibis, decode secret messages and discover hidden details that can change the course of the investigation;

POVESTEA CAZULUI

&Icirc;n noaptea de 9 martie 1930, un eveniment tragic a avut loc &icirc;n incinta faimosului ospiciu Obregia. Igor Malenovschi, un pacient &icirc;nchis &icirc;n salonul de maximă securitate, a fost găsit mort &icirc;n circumstanțe misterioase. &Icirc;n roluri de detectivi, sunteți chemați să puneți cap la cap indiciile și să dezvăluiți identitatea criminalului. Printre suspecții principali se numără pacienții internați &icirc;n aripa B a ospiciului, acolo unde erau ținuți cei mai agresivi dintre aceștia. Veți putea aduna și conecta informațiile necesare pentru a face lumină &icirc;n acest caz enigmatic? Ce legătură ar putea avea moartea lui Igor Malenovschi cu trecutul său &icirc;ntunecat? Toate răspunsurile se ascund &icirc;n coridoarele &icirc;ntunecate ale ospiciului, iar misiunea voastră este să le aduceți &icirc;n lumina adevărului. Intrați &icirc;n lumea &icirc;nfricoșătoare a ospiciului Obregia pentru a face dreptate lui Igor Malenovschi, ale cărui secrete &icirc;ncă așteaptă să fie dezvăluite!

CASE STORY

The discovery of a body just a few steps from the Witches' Pond causes a wave of anxiety among the locals who no longer believe in the long-forgotten legends of this mysterious place. Is it a cold-blooded murder or a ritual that breaks the barriers of the paranormal? The verdict of the investigators is reserved until the arrival of your team of detectives, who have proven at every opportunity that nothing is what it seems. Thus, you receive for examination this box that once belonged to the victim. By piecing together the evidence obtained and questioning the suspects in the victim's circle of relations, will you be able to unravel the mystical universe of Elisa Adamache and unravel the curses of the Witches' Swamp?

- Investigation game in which you take on the role of a detective to solve an unsolved case;

- Analyze evidence, eliminate suspects and identify the criminal;

- Browse social networks, check suspects' alibis, decode secret messages and discover hidden details that can change the course of the investigation;

POVESTEA CAZULUI

Găsirea unui cadavru la doar c&acirc;țiva pași de Balta Vrăjitoarelor st&acirc;rnește un val de neliniște &icirc;n r&acirc;ndul localnicilor care nu mai cred &icirc;n legendele demult uitate ale acestui loc misterios. Să fie vorba de o crimă cu s&acirc;nge rece sau de un ritual ce rupe barierele paranormalului? Verdictul anchetatorilor răm&acirc;ne rezervat p&acirc;nă la sosirea echipei voastre de detectivi, care a dovedit cu fiecare ocazie că nimic nu este ce pare a fi. Astfel, primiți spre examinare această cutie ce a aparținut c&acirc;ndva victimei. Pun&acirc;nd cap la cap probele obținute și interog&acirc;nd suspecții din cercul de relații al victimei, veți putea dezvălui universul mistic al Elisei Adamache și dezlega blestemele Bălții Vrăjitoarelor?

CASE STORY

A grand hotel becomes the scene of a tragedy that casts a shadow over its former reputation. The night before the premiere, Selena Dima, a young actress, ends up breathless in the elevator shaft of the Cișmigiu Hotel, without any obvious explanation. In the absence of relevant evidence and a culprit, the investigation was closed by the authorities. The management of Cișmigiu Hotel asks for your help in the hope that you will be helpful in saving its prestige. Will you be able to piece together the evidence to uncover the thread of the events of that night and make the untold story of Selena Dima heard?

- Investigation game in which you take on the role of a detective to solve an unsolved case;

- Analyze evidence, eliminate suspects and identify the criminal;

- Browse social networks, check suspects' alibis, decode secret messages and discover hidden details that can change the course of the investigation;

POVESTEA CAZULUI

Un hotel grandios devine scena unei tragedii ce a pus &icirc;n umbră reputația sa de odinioară. Cu o noapte &icirc;naintea premierei, Selena Dima, o t&acirc;nără actriță, sf&acirc;rșește fără suflare &icirc;n puțul liftului Hotelului Cișmigiu, fără vreo explicație evidentă. &Icirc;n lipsa unor probe relevante și a unui vinovat, ancheta a fost &icirc;nchisă de către autorități. Conducerea Hotelului Cișmigiu vă solicită ajutorul &icirc;n speranța că veți fi de ajutor &icirc;n salvarea prestigiului său. Veți putea pune cap la cap dovezile pentru a scoate la lumină firul evenimentelor din acea noapte și a face auzită povestea nespusă a Selenei Dima?

CASE STORY

A team of American researchers is called to elucidate the paranormal phenomena of the Hoia-Baciu Forest, known for hundreds of years. A rock festival that could not be postponed disrupts the investigation and creates favorable conditions for a perfect murder. Shortly after moving the camp, Professor Magnus Jefferson, a genius of modern science, is killed in the very heart of the forest. The forester's fingerprints were found on the murder weapon, but the teacher's apprentice is not convinced that he is the culprit and asks you and your team to help solve the case. Will you be able to solve the case in time and find the real killer?

- Investigation game in which you take on the role of a detective to solve an unsolved case;

- Analyze evidence, eliminate suspects and identify the criminal;

- Browse social networks, check suspects' alibis, decode secret messages and discover hidden details that can change the course of the investigation;

POVESTEA CAZULUI

O echipă de cercetători americani este chemată pentru a elucida fenomenele paranormale ale Pădurii Hoia-Baciu, cunoscute de sute de ani. Un festival rock ce nu a putut fi am&acirc;nat perturbă cercetările și creează condițiile favorabile pentru o crimă perfectă. La scurt timp după mutarea taberei, profesorul Magnus Jefferson, un geniu al științei moderne, este ucis chiar &icirc;n inima pădurii. Amprentele pădurarului au fost găsite pe arma crimei, &icirc;nsă ucenicul profesorului nu este convins că acesta ar fi vinovatul și te roagă pe tine și pe echipa ta de detectivi să interveniți &icirc;n rezolvarea cazului. Vei putea să rezolvi cazul la timp și să găsești adevăratul criminal?

Battles for Quebec is Clash of Arms' tenth installment of the award-winning "Battles in the Age of Reason" (BAR) series. It includes three battles and seven scenarios.

The Plains of Abraham(13 september 1759). This includes the famous morning clash on the heights: Montcalm vs. Wolfe. It also includes a scenario that starts with the first British landing, in which gamers play out the entire day's battle and see what could have happened.

Sainte Foy (29 April 1760). Three scenarios represent this largely forgotten battle in which the French had one last chance to defeat the British and possibly retake Quebec. This is a classic BAR battle on the frozen plains outside Quebec.

Assault on Quebec (31 December 1775). In a very different battle for the series, American forces are trying to assault Quebec at night in a blizzard. The fate of the fourteenth colony is at stake. This close battle will challenge the most experienced BAR gamers, and includes a scenario with hiden forces for a complete fog of war experience.

Meticulously researched, including the use of primary sources to determine the delicatedeatils of the battles, Battles for Quebec is a thorough treatment of these battles, represented at a depth that has never been seen before in wargaming.

Components:

        BAR Standard Series Rules booklet (v3.4);
        Battles for Quebec game-specific rules booklet;
        Battles for Quebec game-specific charts and tables;
        One 22" x 34" full color, period-style map;
        420 1/2" Counters, both full color and black & white;
        Cardstock diagrams and displays;
        Two ten-sided dice.


&mdash;description from Clash of Arms website

Embark on a journey through SLO CAL, the gem of California's central coast, in this special edition of Monopoly. San Luis Obispo County, perfectly poised halfway between Los Angeles and San Francisco, offers a unique escape into a world where natural beauty and a laid-back lifestyle converge. With over 315 days of sunshine annually, SLO CAL is a year-round haven for adventure, relaxation, and culinary delights.

In this game, you'll traverse picturesque landscapes, from serene beaches to rolling vineyards, capturing the essence of small-town charm combined with diverse cultural experiences. SLO CAL isn't just a destination; it's a celebration of life lived at a leisurely pace, where every moment is cherished, and connections deepen.

Discover the region's enchanting communities, each radiating its own character and allure. From the vibrant farm-to-table scene to the breathtaking dunes and turquoise waters, SLO CAL is a mosaic of life's finest pleasures. Join us in this Monopoly edition and experience the unique magic of a region where &ldquo;Life's Too Beautiful to Rush.&rdquo;

2D6 Dungeon Lair Expansion Vol 2 &ndash; the adventure continues&hellip;

Most mine shafts that are found in the land have collapsed and cannot be entered. But the Ancient Mine Shaft was well established and has a complex network of deep rooms on three levels. These abandoned locations are feared by locals and can be a place where subterranean creatures have penetrated or sought shelter and must be cleared to remove the threat to the land.

In the west of Adrumar, in the region that borders the Heartland, are the Basins of Adrumar. They were formed by an earthquake many centuries ago when rock formations were revealed by sinking sands. They are a network of open top rooms set in uneven sandstone chambers sculpted by Kaladear herself during the creation of the world.

A German party game for people with a crude sense of humor! It can't get much stupider than that! For fans of the German TV show Joko&Klaas &ldquo;Liebes Tagebuch!&rdquo;
The new fun card game with simple rules - learned in 1 minute. Contents: 440 wild playing cards that can create 3.58 trillion (no joke) different combinations. The funniest sentence wins. Who wins most cards is the hero of the game.

&mdash;description from the publisher

Ein deutsches Partyspiel f&uuml;r Leute mit einem derben Sinn f&uuml;r Humor! Viel d&uuml;mmer geht es nicht! F&uuml;r Fans der deutschen TV-Show Joko&Klaas &bdquo;Liebes Tagebuch!&ldquo;
Das neue lustige Kartenspiel mit einfachen Regeln &ndash; in 1 Minute erlernt. Inhalt: 440 Wild-Spielkarten, die 3,58 Billionen (kein Scherz) verschiedene Kombinationen bilden k&ouml;nnen. Der lustigste Satz gewinnt. Wer die meisten Karten gewinnt, ist der Held des Spiels.

&mdash;description from the publisher (German)

This exciting new Birds of Prey product features an in-depth analysis of the kinematic performance of the AIM-4 Falcon family, with a focus on the reasoning behind the F-106's Super Falcon missiles. The product also includes all the scenarios and aircraft from the 2023 Birds of Prey Convention, and an account of the event, including the famous Kangaroo Court and call-sign assignments. There is one other extra-special aircraft data card, continuing our series featuring target types.

